Do I say this right? – Syntax checking - ansible-playbook --syntax-check playbook.yml 
Whom am I talking to? – Listing affected hosts - ansible-playbook --list-hosts playbook.yml 
What’s going on here? – List tasks - ansible-playbook --list-tasks playbook.yml
What’s that thing? – List all tags -  ansible-playbook --list-tags
Are you sure? – Running in test mode -  ansible-playbook --check  playbook.yml
Let me have a look at that… – Going through tasks step by step - ansible-playbook --step
